{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"inheritsFrom","kind":"relationships","title":"Inherits From","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/10GLibObject0B0C"]},{"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserverProtocol","doc:\/\/GIO\/4GLib14PointerWrapperP","doc:\/\/GIO\/10GLibObject0B8ProtocolP"],"kind":"relationships"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/dbusauthobserver"]}],"abstract":[{"code":"GDBusAuthObserver","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" provides a mechanism for participating"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in how a [class","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusServer","isActive":true},{"text":"] (or a [class","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection","isActive":true},{"text":"])","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"authenticates remote peers."}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Class","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"DBusAuthObserver"}],"title":"DBusAuthObserver","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO16DBusAuthObserverC","symbolKind":"class","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"DBusAuthObserver","kind":"identifier"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"DBusAuthObserver","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Simply instantiate a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusAuthObserver"},{"type":"text","text":" and connect to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"signals you are interested in. Note that new signals may be added"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in the future.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Controlling Authentication Mechanisms","anchor":"Controlling-Authentication-Mechanisms"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusServer"},{"text":" or server-side ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusConnection"},{"type":"text","text":" will allow"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"any authentication mechanism to be used. If you only want to allow D-Bus","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connections with the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"EXTERNAL"},{"type":"text","text":" mechanism, which makes use of credentials"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"passing and is the recommended mechanism for modern Unix platforms such"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"as Linux and the BSD family, you would use a signal handler like this:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"c","code":["static gboolean","on_allow_mechanism (GDBusAuthObserver *observer,","                    const gchar       *mechanism,","                    gpointer           user_data)","{","  if (g_strcmp0 (mechanism, \"EXTERNAL\") == 0)","    {","      return TRUE;","    }","","  return FALSE;","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Controlling Authorization","anchor":"Controlling-Authorization"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusServer"},{"text":" or server-side ","type":"text"},{"code":"GDBusConnection","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will accept"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connections from any successfully authenticated user (but not from"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"anonymous connections using the "},{"code":"ANONYMOUS","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" mechanism). If you only"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"want to allow D-Bus connections from processes owned by the same uid"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"as the server, since GLib 2.68, you should use the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"G_DBUS_SERVER_FLAGS_AUTHENTICATION_REQUIRE_SAME_USER","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" flag. It’s equivalent"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to the following signal handler:"}]},{"syntax":"c","code":["static gboolean","on_authorize_authenticated_peer (GDBusAuthObserver *observer,","                                 GIOStream         *stream,","                                 GCredentials      *credentials,","                                 gpointer           user_data)","{","  gboolean authorized;","","  authorized = FALSE;","  if (credentials != NULL)","    {","      GCredentials *own_credentials;","      own_credentials = g_credentials_new ();","      if (g_credentials_is_same_user (credentials, own_credentials, NULL))","        authorized = TRUE;","      g_object_unref (own_credentials);","    }","","  return authorized;","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver"},{"type":"text","text":" type acts as a reference-counted owner of an underlying "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusAuthObserver"},{"type":"text","text":" instance."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"It provides the methods that can operate on this data type through ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserverProtocol","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" conformance.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" as a strong reference or owner of a "},{"code":"GDBusAuthObserver","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instance.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserverRef"},{"type":"text","text":" (instead of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver","isActive":true},{"text":") for a lightweight Swift reference to an underlying ","type":"text"},{"code":"GDBusAuthObserver","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instance.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside"}]}],"sections":[],"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver\/init()","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver\/init(_:)-4qrkc","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver\/init(_:)-5dv8g","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver\/init(_:)-7nww7","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver\/init(_:)-j4s6","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver\/init(cPointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver\/init(dBusAuthObserver:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver\/init(gconstpointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver\/init(gpointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver\/init(opaquePointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver\/init(raw:)-2phd4","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver\/init(raw:)-8u87q","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver\/init(retaining:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver\/init(retainingCPointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver\/init(retainingOpaquePointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusAuthObserver\/init(retainingRaw:)-3xby2","doc:\/\/